{"tid":1426631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛郎織女，今晚快閃睇星 !","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:14.000Z","uid":184576,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1a89bc449a8a2d67556ed42144b4f068d922d3","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:21.000Z","msg":"因為香港天氣變化快，所以香港天文發燒友會係有特別天象時，係同好之間舉行「快閃觀星」；如果有包含可普羅大眾推廣作用，就會叫「路邊天文」，太空館同香港各大天文組織年中不時都會舉辦。<br />\n<br />\n「快閃觀星」和「路邊天文」會視乎情況、當晚主題帶備不同種類望遠鏡(可以是大型望遠鏡觀看深空天體，或是手持雙筒望遠鏡，亦可以乜都唔帶用肉眼睇)和同好及公眾分享。如果附近市民有興趣，不少天文發燒友會友善的向市民講解。當講解時需要指星，用手指會很麻煩，不少天文發燒友就會用到綠色鐳射筆(因為在夜晚人眼對綠光相對敏感，所以觀星用的大多是綠色)。<br />\n<br />\n今天適逢農曆七夕，入黑後可以看到夏季大三角中的牛郎織女星。如果認得出牛郎織女星，一定會是個非常浪漫的七夕！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲買齊觀星器材啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf0f2b1ee24299215e3e221bf5c92b37baad1c6","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"2af4d523cfb3600edfafce99cfdb314c175eeb22","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"開錯台添"},{"pid":"6a02d3221ffdedf2a9057fcbe8c2d37b7e3c5115","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"upup"},{"pid":"991180d46c0e77f1d04136b7f78b1a96764e51cd","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc63582bfe253ac7bc88e6b6f38bbb984f44a3ee","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"睇靚靚星"},{"pid":"b81ee8684a2026885c951b3b034a00466fe389e9","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"upppp"},{"pid":"91a0913588e08a8fe04b0f60d47c8f90623bb460","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d880e8f4478770ba731e9ae14a4404fe031a3861","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:48.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"891a4965cdbca5988cb572a020395b9a0743785b","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:02.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3c6e9a03b6858fa6a605be6d706d6921b68683a7","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"33d3cd9f54ab736ad53b1f048f9d25c2430cd60a","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e082273682c1a5d814f1f1dcefb30acc0e0b6b07","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"90637b87811b648932f0e2e65a1425c3ff4ddd9b","tid":1426631,"uid":184576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:14.000Z","msg":"5"}]}